SELECT * FROM gold_sales.dbo.dimsalesperson


SELECT
DISTINCT YEAR(OrderDate) 
FROM gold_sales.dbo.factorder


SELECT 
SalesPersonId, SUM(SubTotal) AS Sales
FROM silver_sales.dbo.salesorderheader
WHERE YEAR(OrderDate) = 2014
GROUP BY SalesPersonID
ORDER BY SUM(SubTotal) DESC

SELECT * FROM silver_sales.
